  "response": "\"Recipient name\" refers to the name of the person or entity that is intended to receive something, such as a piece of mail, a package, a payment, or any type of delivery. In contexts like mailing or shipping, the recipient name is usually written on the address label to ensure that the item reaches the correct individual or organization.",
